# VCSL Keys source archive (~650MB, CC0; not redistributed via this repo).
# Download it yourself from https://versilian-studios.com/vcsl-keys/ and
# drop it at this path before running `cargo xtask prepare-vcsl-piano`.
/docs/VCSL_Keys.zip

# Generated VCSL sampler bank (large; regenerate via `cargo xtask prepare-vcsl-piano`).
# The small dev bank is committed: z-audio-webclap-vcsl-piano embeds it at build time.
/assets/vcsl-piano/grand-piano-k.bank
